g.aria-label: A skin for chipsynth SFC. Please note that this skin is NOT an official skin, and not supported by Plogue in any way. Please do not contact Plogue if you have nay issues with it. This skin was designed for use on chipsynth SFC V1.023. While I did test it on both Windows and Mac, there are rendering differences between the two due to the engines on each platform being slightly different. This skin is intended mostly for the Windows port but should work on Mac. I will attempt to keep it up to date when new versions of chipsynth SFC are released. Special thanks to David from Plogue for putting up with my questions. chipsynth SFC and all chipsynth variants are trademarked by Plogue Art et Technologie, Inc. 2005-2020
